    "cultural_notes": "While not a deeply traditional dish, pineapple rice is a popular modern home-cooked meal in Uganda that makes creative use of locally abundant pineapples. It represents the adaptability of Ugandan cuisine, incorporating tropical fruits into everyday meals. It's often prepared for guests or on weekends when families have more time to cook."
